3.7 Definition Let $\langle S, *\rangle$ and $\left\langle S^{\prime}, *^{\prime}\right\rangle$ be binary algebraic structures. An isomorphism of $S$ with $S^{\prime}$ is a one-to-one function $\phi$ mapping $S$ onto $S^{\prime}$ such that

$$
